{
  "stem": "11175.5",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "As I'm talking to myself, so quiet, I grabbed my pants, and I started to run.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I started to run, feel the first bullet here.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "You see?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "[POINTS] The marks is-- is still here.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "[POINTING] And I-- and I fell down.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I-- I couldn't hold up my pants.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I fell down, and I'm laying.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Two minutes, three minutes later, an SS man, a Ukrainian, came over to me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "He looked at me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Are you alive?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "You son of a this, this, and this.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "You're alive.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And he took that rifle and put it right over here.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I have these marks here, you see?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "[POINTS] He took that rifle and aimed it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And then, bingo, he shot.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And it looks like the bullet went down here and didn't hit that nerve.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "[STAMMERS] And-- and I laid down, and the blood started to run.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And I'm laying.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "In a minute, two minutes later, I hear-- [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH] [MAKES MACHINE GUN NOISES] [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH] He shot them.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And then, nine minutes later, and I felt the drop after drop of blood coming out.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And I-- I'm afraid to move in that place, because if I'm going to move in that place, then somebody will notice that.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And them guys are going to shot me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In front of me, what-- this looks like-- then somebody else was running with me also, because I heard, in the back of me, one is laying, [MOANING] And it got quieter, quieter.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It looks like he was shot with that running.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he died in that place.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was laying there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was laying about two-- more than two hours-- more than two hours, until they finished all the people there.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This was about 700 people.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
